response.joke: I used to play piano by ear, but now I use my hands. It's much more effective at parties.
Why don't skeletons fight each other at parties? They don't have the guts.
I went to a party last night and lost my watch, but I'm sure I'll have a good time finding it.
I'm reading a book on anti-gravity. It's impossible to put down! Classic dad material.
Did you hear about the restaurant on the moon? Great food, no atmosphere. Such a dad joke!
Why did the scarecrow win an award? Because he was outstanding in his field! Oh, dads love this one.
